performance of ballet comique de la reine , the first narrative ballet , devised by louise of lorraine , wife of henry iii of france , and choreographed by balthasar de beaujoyeulx , opens at the court of catherine de ' medici in the louvre palace in paris as part of the wedding celebrations for marguerite of lorraine .

